評民進黨沒有知會立法院，擺明硬幹，質疑是黨意凌駕民意。前總統馬英九辦公室亦指，蔡英文過去帶頭反對開放美國豬牛輸入，如今在沒有通知立法院，也沒有同畜牧業者溝通的情況下擴大開放，應該為雙重標準與髮夾彎，向社會大眾道歉。<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"> 在北京，國台辦發言人馬曉光回應指，民進黨當局不顧民意反對，為政治目的執意開放有問題的美國農畜產品進口，損害島內民眾的健康福祉，</span></span>借機換取外部勢力對台獨勢力的支持，勢必遭到兩岸同胞的堅決反對 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china23547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina23547&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=b1aab5d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china23547</a><p class=\"left\"></p>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"台灣買美國牛肉關支那撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fb149bcb51b39deba370291d233d249d3b75fb","tid":2178604,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"慣性用支那視角報國際新聞係咩玩法？"},{"pid":"6e084e2c50f6967cbfd8c200aa2e207792b11748","tid":2178604,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe223551546e7512c43d310f93badd6c2d202169","tid":2178604,"uid":21545,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"關支那咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"乜都用支那視角報，垃圾港媒"},{"pid":"1c2f0db7d5be46a8814836e31cd02828302ba3a9","tid":2178604,"uid":333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"食美國牛都要干涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135d851069c291652d0aaf5e12c09e9b2403e336","tid":2178604,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f880211b7ddc5b6c980a5ebdd93618f130dc59a0","tid":2178604,"uid":177039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"終於有人講呢單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上美國同台灣好有可能係11月大選之前簽到FTA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" cla